HMAC384 Key Vault Control Register

Absolute Address:
Base Offset:
0x200
Size:
0x4

Description

Controls the Key Vault access for HMAC384

Contents

Bits Identifier Access Reset Decoded Name
[31] dest_done rw 0x0 -
[30] src_done rw 0x0 -
[29] key_done rw 0x0 -
[28:27] rsvd1 rw 0x0 -
[26:24] dest_valid rw 0x0 -
[23:21] rsvd_dest_sel rw 0x0 -
[20] dest_sel_pcr rw 0x0 -
[19:17] dest_sel rw 0x0 -
[16] dest_sel_en rw 0x0 -
[15:13] src_data_size rw 0x0 -
[12] src_sel_pcr rw 0x0 -
[11:9] src_sel rw 0x0 -
[8] src_sel_en rw 0x0 -
[7:5] rsvd_key_sel rw 0x0 -
[4] key_sel_pcr rw 0x0 -
[3:1] key_sel rw 0x0 -
[0] key_sel_en rw 0x0 -

Field Descriptions

dest_done

Result has been copied to key vault

src_done

Source has been copied from key vault to engine

key_done

Key has been copied form key vault to engine

rsvd1

Reserved field

dest_valid

Destination valid bits. Determines where the result of the crypto function can be used after being stored in the key vault.

rsvd_dest_sel

Reserved field

dest_sel_pcr

Destination selected is a PCR slot

dest_sel

Key Vault entry to store the result

dest_sel_en

Indicates that the result is to be stored in the key vault

src_data_size

Size of the source data for padding function. Size is encoded as N-1 128 bits of data. Padding is generated for size values 0-5.

src_sel_pcr

Source selected is a PCR slot

src_sel

Key Vault entry to retrieve the source for the engine

src_sel_en

Indicates that the source value is to come from the key vault

rsvd_key_sel

Reserved field

key_sel_pcr

Key selected is a PCR slot

key_sel

Key Vault entry to retrieve the key for the engine

key_sel_en

Indicates that the key value is to come from the key vault
